properties.name: presentation
properties.description: If true, the file type is presentation. If false, the file type is Multi-Page document.

properties.name: autoAdvance
properties.description: If true, the presentation auto advances.

properties.name: interval
properties.description: The amount of time (in seconds) before auto advancing the view. Valid only when 'auto advance' is true. Range: 1 to 60.

properties.name: loop
properties.description: If true, the presentation loops after the last page.

properties.name: magnification
properties.description: The magnification type when viewing the image.

properties.name: includeFilename
properties.description: If true, includes the file name for the image.

properties.name: PDFFileOptions
properties.description: Options for creating the PDF file.

name: PresentationOptions
description: Options for the PDF presentation command.
